org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.filespecs

Class SWCFileSpecification

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.filespecs.SWCFileSpecification
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IBinaryFileSpecification, IFileSpecification

    public class SWCFileSpecification
extends Object
implements IBinaryFileSpecification
    A SWCFileSpecification allows us to attach read a file from a SWC. This allows us to treat the SWC as one FileSpec
